{"tid":1762610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周同學嘅安息禮好早已經有人幫緊，事實上唔喺寶福出殯仲好","createTime":"2019-11-29T16:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T08:02:11.000Z","uid":64232,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a28df79ed43dee389a744d38e2d6d36e9bf62e5d","tid":1762610,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"寶福話全行都唔會幫佢，係講大話，根本唔使理，<br />\n事實上喺連登出Post前，已經有人幫緊家人，所以我相信個禮係無問題的<br />\n其實周同學唔喺寶福出殯仲好，貪佢又殘又舊又成日勒索咩<br />\n我死咗邊個送我去寶福我實斬開佢九碌<br />\n知道大家好嬲，但已經好多人幫緊家人，就交畀專業去做，各位手足唔好咁擔心<br />\n低調啲，畀家人可以順利送周同學最後一程先係最重要"},{"pid":"075f7b72993369782d7042a264c8c1b20f8876d8","tid":1762610,"uid":80566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"西樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好火遮眼，補完血記住推行動post"},{"pid":"cd5d1142d521c5d64543c50cb175b5fefdb3f9b1","tid":1762610,"uid":46814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T17:05:30.000Z","msg":"連西樓都出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b022b3215d0a8d912559a59f2acc27beef8842","tid":1762610,"uid":64232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cd5d1142d521c5d64543c50cb175b5fefdb3f9b1","tid":1762610,"uid":46814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T17:05:30.000Z","msg":"連西樓都出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"見家人想低調，但無計大家太嬲<br />\n都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9dbd21ed2026d86735cb83e11db78607564f1e","tid":1762610,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"Gay廉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9d36c2f12e8d51d41e3a9ca4c7ebfa9844e3f2","tid":1762610,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"咪係囉"},{"pid":"8fd851da9